                    <p class="text-big text-bold text-uppercase">Bitcoin - There Can Only be One</p>
                    <p>Dominance is back to 70%, which begs the following question: is it just getting started as it surpasses it's former status (pre-2017 bubble) or will the Alt Season come back? This presentation will thoroughly demonstrate how Altcoins like Litecoin &amp; Monero and Blockchians like Ethereum &amp; Cordana are truly shitcoins and the only path for them is towards a value of 0.</p>
