                  <div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-10">
                    <p class="text-big text-bold text-uppercase">OPT-OUT: Russian consequences</p>
                    <p>After fall of Soviet Union and years of political freedom most Russian people opted out of political life. It appears there are a lot more interesting things to do: travel, develop technologies, create the art, grew up children.<br><br>But there were some others, who have not opted out of the race for powers. <br><br>What do we have now in Russia, what about OPT-OUT now?</p>
