                  <div class="col-xs-8 col-sm-10">
                    <p class="text-big text-bold text-uppercase">OpenDEX - A Protocol for Unstoppable P2P Trading</p>
                    <p>The talk covers architecture design choices, the different layers involved, the p2p messaging layer and discusses scalability. The second part demos a trade of an implementation implementing the OpenDEX protocol, an atomic swap between Bitcoin and DAI, a USD stablecoin via the Lightning and Raiden Network. The last part discusses the transition to a community-driven, open &amp; token free protocol and gives a glimpse into implications for society.</p>
