                    <p class="text-big text-bold text-uppercase">Panel - Crypto Liberation Communities meetup</p>
                    <p>Let us introduce existing Crypto Liberation Communities in Catalonia, Germany, Austria, Czech Republic and Slovakia.<br><br>Listen their short stories, their achievements and fails.<br><br>Be inspired and create your own community!<br><br>Panelists:<br>Nelson Melina &amp; Marc Guals - Barcelona's Polis Parallela <br>Joerg Platzer - Room 77<br>Gideon Gallasch - Bitcoin enthusiast, Co-Founder Blockchainhotel and Bitcoin-Treff.de<br>Smuggler - Anarplex.net / Berlin Container<br>Martin Leskovjan - Prague's Paralelní Polis<br>Juraj Bednár - Bratislava's Paralelná Polis<br>Tomas Kanócz - Košice's Paralelná polis<br><br>Moderated by: Pavol Lupták</p>
