                    <p class="text-big text-bold text-uppercase">Workshop - How to Crack a Private Key</p>
                    <p>How to Crack a Private Key<br>Lead by Robin Cussol<br><br>Most people take for granted that cryptography and maths secure billions of dollars worth of cryptocurrency assets everyday, but have you ever asked yourself, “How?”. During this workshop you will learn how – by attempting to crack a private key given its public key using only maths.<br><br>Prerequisites Knowledge<br>Basic mathematics including algebra<br><br>About Robin Cussol<br>After completing a PhD in Mathematics, Robin decided to apply his logical mind to impact more people through software development. He now spends most of his time coding web and mobile applications, but still enjoys the odd occasion to do some maths and explain arcane symbols.</p>
