                    <p class="text-big text-bold text-uppercase">Dishonest Devs: Defeating Insider Attacks on Decentralized Tech</p>
                    <p>Decentralized systems are meant to be trustless. But our interactions with tech is always mediated by software. This talk will cover the threat, including real and hypothetical attacks, what it takes for communities to defeat these attacks, and how we can better design decentralized systems to defeat these attacks.</p>
